  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "Cut zucchini into small cubes and squeeze out excess moisture. Mix with the drained tofu.",
    "Add lime juice, orange zest, and coriander; mix well until no lumps remain.",
    "Transfer mixture to a baking dish and bake for 45 minutes or until p\u00e2t\u00e9 reaches desired consistency.",
    "Allow it to cool before garnishing with sesame seeds if desired.",
    "Serve as a side dish or spread over crackers."
